Context: The George Brown College offers an Online Hearing Instrument Specialist (S117) program. Students can contact Constantine Karolidis at ckarolid@georgebrown.ca for more information. Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other related information can be obtained by signing up on the website. The college's contact numbers are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559, and students may reach out via email at ask.george@georgebrown.ca or visit the Social Media Hub for more information. The content of the website is subject to change without notice. Prospective students are advised to verify the college fees.
